s 8)","source":"[Stack Based Failure Injection](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Hh974664) (Windows 8)"},{"content":"The <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Stack Based Failure Injection<ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Hh974664)</ept> option injects resource failures in kernel-mode drivers.","pos":[10394,10554],"source":"The [Stack Based Failure Injection](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Hh974664) option injects resource failures in kernel-mode drivers."},{"content":"This option uses a special driver, KmAutoFail.sys, in conjunction with <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Driver Verifier<ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448)</ept> to penetrate driver error handling paths.","pos":[10555,10753],"source":" This option uses a special driver, KmAutoFail.sys, in conjunction with [Driver Verifier](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff545448) to penetrate driver error handling paths."},{"pos":[10759,10988],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Note<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>  You cannot combine <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>Stack Based Failure Injection<ept id=\"p2\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Hh974664)</ept> with <bpt id=\"p3\">[</bpt>Low resources simulation<ept id=\"p3\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff548288)</ept>.","source":"**Note**  You cannot combine [Stack Based Failure Injection](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Hh974664) with [Low resources simulation](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff548288)."},{"pos":[11213,11266],"content":"Driver Verifier options that require I/O Verification"},{"content":"There are four options that require you to first enable <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>I/O Verification<ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/Library/Windows/Hardware/Ff548045)</ept>.","pos":[11538,11681],"source":"There are four options that